highlights.text: “back to friends” by sombr has been on Viral Songs Global the longest, at 135 days straight.
“davina mccall” by Wet Leg is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Global at #92.
KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Global. “Golden” is the highest at #1.
“Charger” by TRIANGLE DES BERMUDES, MC YOSHI, Mauvais djo, and Kokosvoice is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Global, up 9 spots at #29.
